"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-sodexo-live-royal-ascot-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Bethany Wales  From theParis Olympicsand the Rugby World Cup to Royal Ascot, Sodexo Live has become the invisible force keeping plates loaded and champagne glasses topped up at Europe's biggest events.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 208, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ascot_Racecourse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0929193064732435e-39, \"text\": \"Royal Ascot\", \"types\": [\"Q1777138\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ascot_Racecourse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ascot_Racecourse\"}, {\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023 the Paris-headquarteredcatering giant's events division, Sodexo Live, served more than 11m guests in the UK alone, employing around 1,700 people across the country to keep its operations running.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.961897908133319, \"rank\": 0.039611367843202384, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite a tough couple of years that saw the Covid-19 pandemic wipe out live events, Sodexo's London-headquartered UK arm has rebounded in spectacular fashion, reporting record turnover of \\u00a31.4bn in the year ending August 31, 2023, up from \\u00a31.2bn in the same period of 2019, according to itsmost recently-filed accounts.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.961897908133319, \"rank\": 0.039611367843202384, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This increase in sales has delivered a much-needed boost to the company's recovering bottom line, with its pre-tax profit reaching \\u00a351m in its latest financial year, inching closer to the \\u00a382m it hit in the 12 months ending August 31, 2019.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But according to Claire Morris, Sodexo Live's UK CEO, returning to its pre-pandemic profit levels is just the starting point for the company's ambitious growth plans.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}, {\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.961897908133319, \"rank\": 0.039611367843202384, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay ahead with our three daily briefings delivering all the key market moves, top business and political stories, and incisive analysis straight to your inbox.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Growth is absolutely a top priority for us and it's going to happen in two ways\\\", she said.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Firstly we are out there to win new clients which is about showing them our proven track record of delivering what we say we will.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Secondly, we are going to focus on enhancing our services for existing clients.\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, if we are already providing retail services, we can expand our offerings to include hospitality, and vice versa.\\\"\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This strategy was demonstrated recently when Sodexo Live's long-time client,Hampden Park stadium in Glasgow, asked the firm to take over the running of its non-match day events in addition to the retail and hospitality it provides during games.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1931, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}, {\"begin\": 1986, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999999995220605, \"rank\": 4.676371195453658e-10, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morris said: \\\"Our work at Hampden Park is a great example of how we can work with clients to identify their pain points and say OK, here's a different way we can help you reach your goals.\\\"\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With such a broad range of clients looking for everything from fast food to Michelin star dining, Morris said the key to Sodexo Live's success has been its ability to shape shift.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}, {\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}, {\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company'sRoyal Ascotoffering is the perfect example of this superpower.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the most recent five day meeting Sodexo Live provided catering for more than 250,000 people across 20 restaurants, made possible by at least 3,500 members of staff per day.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Morris said: \\\"Those five days are the pinnacle of the British summer event's calendar and we have to make sure there is something for everyone.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2762, \"end\": 2768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}, {\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999840079, \"rank\": 1.5787416398787315e-08, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We operate four different enclosures, with the Royal enclosure at the premium end.\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2955, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fasil_Ghebbi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal enclosure\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fasil_Ghebbi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fasil_Ghebbi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where you are seeing guests in their top hats and tails who are paying for hospitality.\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Within that they have a choice of restaurants run by chefs like Simon Rogan, who has three Michelin stars, and of course our long-standing partner Raymond Blanc.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3179, \"end\": 3187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 0.999613755119758, \"rank\": 0.0003863941227750781, \"text\": \"Michelin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}, {\"begin\": 3235, \"end\": 3248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Raymond Blanc\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raymond_Blanc\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Guests can also opt for a high-end retail option which is going to include things like steak sandwiches or a luxury afternoon tea so it's still in keeping with the environment.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then in the Queen Anne enclosure you are going to see mainly retail offerings but guests also have the option to buy a hospitality experience with Lisa Goodwin Allen, who also has a Michelin star.\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3578, \"end\": 3582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999997987593108, \"rank\": 2.0124066365915079e-07, \"text\": \"Lisa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisa_Simpson\"}, {\"begin\": 3591, \"end\": 3596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"score\": 0.9999999998403837, \"rank\": 1.5711622628589128e-10, \"text\": \"Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\"}, {\"begin\": 3613, \"end\": 3626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michelin star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelin_Guide\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People looking for something more low-key are also going to find what they are looking for across our retail kiosks, whether that's a cup of coffee or a flute of champagne.\\\"\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Sodexo Live, evolving in line with changing consumer expectations has been key to its longevity.\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3809, \"end\": 3815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morris said that as people's budgets have become tighter due to the rising cost of living, the threshold for what counts as good value for money has also been raised.\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 4073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3907, \"end\": 3913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"People do not want to wait in queues and they definitely do not want to miss whatever event they are attending because they are stuck in line for their drinks.\\\"\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To help its staff keep up, Sodexo Live has invested heavily in technology over the past few years, including at Brighton & Hove Albion Football Club, where the company operates food and beverage kiosks.\", \"from\": 4248, \"to\": 4450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4275, \"end\": 4281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morris said: \\\"The club's priority is getting people served fast, so we have introduced 'frictionless' kiosks.\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4452, \"end\": 4458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.9999995022896075, \"rank\": 4.976997863873674e-07, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are fully automated and allow guests to walk up, scan their payment device, grab what they want and then simply walk out to complete their purchase.\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of talk in the industry about how technology and things like self-service is killing hospitality, but we strongly disagree with that.\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We work in many settings where managing queues and providing quick service are crucial, particularly at large music events or football matches, where we are seeing a surge of customers who all need serving within very tight time frames.\", \"from\": 4870, \"to\": 5107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Technology has allowed us to come along leaps and bounds in meeting peoples' changing needs.\\\"\", \"from\": 5109, \"to\": 5203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 5205, \"to\": 5318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5366, \"entities\": []}]}"